selectSql:
select
	c.id id,
	to_date(nullif(c.dataimpressao,''),'YYYYMMDD') data_impressao,
	case when c.impressa = 'S' then true else false end as guia_impressa,
	c.idconsolidacaoarrecadacao id_consolidacao,
	c.idguia id_guia,
	c.idciclo id_periodo,
	null id_usuario_impressao
from consolidacaoarrecadacaohist c
insertSql:
insert into ${SCHEMA}.consolidacao_guia (
	id,
	data_impressao,
	guia_impressa,
	id_consolidacao,
	id_guia,
	id_periodo,
	id_usuario_impressao)
